summary: An ordinance relating to and regulating the conveyance of passengers for hire in the City of Seattle; prescribing minimum and maximum rates therefor; imposing upon the City Comptroller certain duties and powers with respect to the enforcement of Ordinance No. 59866 (as amended) and amending Sections 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 9, 10, 13, 14 and 26 of Ordinance No. 59866.
